新的减持规定正在修改中，那些曾被质疑变相减持的行为，还能继续吗？最严「减持新规」发出两天，约 60 家公司股东终止减持计划 曾经的「花式减持」未来还行得通吗"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1490f72e3cdce1742869cb187f37feaa_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "81 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619831434"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0LiBlJDu5KFPEAMaCTEwMDAyMDI3MSC7m7unBjAAOBxACHIJNjE5ODMxNDM0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1693389789.849759", "card_id": "Q_618928908", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大妈们的衣着打扮为何偏爱艳色？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "大多数退休后的女人都偏爱苹果色系列，这是为何呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/618928908"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I0LiBlJDu5KFPEAMaCDk5ODE5ODQxIIiBnKcGMAA4I0AJcgk2MTg5Mjg5MDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1693389789.850105", "card_id": "Q_619664357", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1171}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价华为 Mate60 Pro 直接开始盲订预约？你会直接盲订吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[6 张图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b862aa9f336f7ee55cb25789b0616538_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619664357"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI